{"tid":2376633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普卸任後首回應記者　「我們會做些事，但不是現在」","createTime":"2021-01-23T03:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T20:54:44.000Z","uid":271829,"like":244,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"c5e4224aea012ba222208d539879542f7ef453da","tid":2376633,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n美國前總統特朗普周三卸任離開白宮後，周五首次在佛羅里達州海湖莊園回應記者提問。特朗普表示：「我們將會做些事，但不是現在。（We&rsquo;ll do something, but not just yet）」霍士新聞指，這反映特朗普對未來有一些計劃，但未準備好開始行動，形容特朗普的未來規劃仍是個謎。<br />\n<br />\n連日打高球歎牛扒<br />\n特朗普周五晚上準備在海湖莊園享用晚餐時，被《華盛頓觀察家報》記者截住及詢問未來大計。雖然特朗普的助手要求記者離開，但特朗普還是作出簡短回應：「我們將會做些事，但不是現在。」他接著便進入餐廳。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210123/RVIAQX5H6RAOTPTMCOEIG7LETE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210123%2FRVIAQX5H6RAOTPTMCOEIG7LETE%2F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5LeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=72598683\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210123%2FRVIAQX5H6RAOTPTMCOEIG7LETE%2F&h=3264e90d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210123/RVIAQX5H6RAOTPTMCOEIG7LETE/</a>"},{"pid":"808b2df9d29b019aeb04b33ba47658431138b3ab","tid":2376633,"uid":93986,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"I still have faith<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797b1ebef60895a136c7722e12cb70f7b1ecca54","tid":2376633,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5b9ac77b2e8ded7138b7473f2323639a8f21a5","tid":2376633,"uid":155095,"like":85,"dislike":3,"score":82,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://metro.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/PRC_171442457.jpg?quality=90&amp;strip=a